label: A5B_oC24_63_afg_c-001
title: $\eta$-Fe$_{2}$Al$_{5}$ Structure
comments:
The Al-I (4a) sites are occupied 34\% of the time, while the Al-III (8g) sites are 24\% occupied, giving a stoichiometry near Fe$_{2}$Al$_{5}$. 
 We have shifted the origin to move the Al-I atom from the (4b) site in (Burkhardt, 1994) to the (4a) site.
